OK where to start ,...well the main video is better than the first cam out,but had issues with interlace,contrast,colours etc....worst part
its missing some video at the end.
Now the conehead video had an extra 35 secs at the end so added that....but that also had issues.

WILL SAY NOW ...STILL MISSING SOME VIDEO!!

Then after some reading i found out there was TWO after credit scenes ...so borrowed them off youtube and added them....yet again both had issues.

Runtime in this release is now 3-4mins longer than all others ( time of writing this of course. )
According to sites offical runtime is 111mins 53 - 1hr 51.53,so still a difference of 14mins,if correct.


WORKDONE -

TOO much ....had to clean all the videos,changing perspectives,fixing ar's,fixing brightness,contrast,rgb colours etc...
Once done it was a case of muxing 4 different videos together,so all had to have the same framerate and res.

Then the audio i had to make complete from 4 different sources,then clean and remaster in AA and resync to my encode.

Could go on and on and trust me there was alot that needed to be done.....
So yes still not full and  i've looked for hrs to find the missing parts but no luck :( ....but we're getting closer now ;-)

Overall v5.5 a5.5 m6
